<p id="mwAkc"><b id="mwAkg">Fort components</b></p>
<div class="div-col columns column-width" style="-moz-column-width: 25em; -webkit-column-width: 25em; column-width: 25em;   " about="#mwt89" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Div col","href":"./Template:Div_col"},"params":{"colwidth":{"wt":"25em"}},"i":0}},"\n* [[Abatis]]\n* [[Banquette]]\n* [[Barbed wire]], [[razor wire]], [[wire entanglement]], and [[wire obstacle]]\n* [[Bartizan]]\n* [[Bastion]]\n* [[Berm]]\n* [[Capital (fortification)|Capital]]\n* [[Caponier]]\n* [[Casemate]]\n* [[Castle walls]]\n* [[Czech hedgehog]]\n* [[Defensive fighting position]]\n* [[Ditch (fortification)|Ditch]]\n* [[Embrasure]]\n* [[Glacis]]\n* [[Gun turret]]\n* [[Keep]]\n* [[Lunette (fortification)|Lunette]]\n* [[Outwork]]\n* [[Palisade]]\n* [[Parapet#Parapets in fortification|Parapet]]\n* [[Pillbox (military)|Pillbox]]\n* [[Postern]]\n* [[Ravelin]]\n* [[Revetment]]\n* [[Sandbag]]\n* [[Sangar (fortification)|Sangar]]\n* [[Counterscarp|Scarp and Counterscarp]]\n* [[Turret]]\n* &apos;&apos;[[Zwinger]]&apos;&apos;\n",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Div col end","href":"./Template:Div_col_end"},"params":{},"i":1}}]}' id="mwAkk">
